consistent hashing is a data partioning and replication solution  where in data servers form a circular ring and store data of a particular range.
consistent hashing mminimizes the keys to be moved in case of node additions or deletions of nodes.
With virtual tokens in picture, we avoud problems like hotspot/celebrity and achieve a more uniform distribution.

